{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":640,"text":"So when I decided to create\nan art piece in Manshiyat Naser,"},{"time":4400,"text":"the neighborhood of the Cairo\ngarbage collectors in Egypt,"},{"time":7400,"text":"I never thought this project would be"},{"time":9240,"text":"the most amazing human experience\nthat I would ever live."},{"time":12640,"text":"As an artist, I had\nthis humanist intention"},{"time":15360,"text":"of beautifying a poor\nand neglected neighborhood"},{"time":17760,"text":"by bringing art to it and hopefully\nshining light on this isolated community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"The first time I heard about\nthis Christian Coptic community"},{"time":27640,"text":"was in 2009 when the Egyptian authorities\nunder the regime of Hosni Mubarak"},{"time":33080,"text":"decided to slaughter 300,000 pigs\nusing the pretext of H1N1 virus."},{"time":39560,"text":"Originally, they are pig breeders."},{"time":41520,"text":"Their pigs and other animals\nare fed with the organic waste"},{"time":44720,"text":"that they collect on a daily basis."},{"time":46720,"text":"This event killed their livelihood."},{"time":49080,"text":"The first time I entered Manshiyat Naser,\nit felt like a maze."},{"time":52560,"text":"I was looking for the St. Simon Monastery\non the top of the Muqattam Mountain."},{"time":56280,"text":"So you go right, then straight,\nthen right again, then left"},{"time":59480,"text":"to reach all the way to the top."},{"time":61200,"text":"But to reach there, you must dodge between\nthe trucks overpacked with garbage"},{"time":65640,"text":"and slalom between the tuk-tuks,"},{"time":67240,"text":"the fastest vehicle to move around\nin the neighborhood."},{"time":71040,"text":"The smell of the garbage\nunloaded from those trucks was intense,"},{"time":74200,"text":"and the noise of the traffic\nwas loud and overbearing."},{"time":77600,"text":"Add to it the din created by the crushers\nin those warehouses along the way."},{"time":82920,"text":"From outside it looks chaotic,\nbut everything is perfectly organized."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88600,"text":"The Zaraeeb, that’s how\nthey call themselves,"},{"time":91080,"text":"which means the pig breeders,"},{"time":92640,"text":"have been collecting the garbage of Cairo"},{"time":95040,"text":"and sorting it in their own\nneighborhood for decades."},{"time":97840,"text":"They have developed\none of the most efficient"},{"time":100000,"text":"and highly profitable systems\non a global level."},{"time":103320,"text":"Still, the place is perceived\nas dirty, marginalized and segregated"},{"time":107960,"text":"because of their association\nwith the trash."},{"time":111080,"text":"So my initial idea\nwas to create an anamorphic piece,"},{"time":113960,"text":"a piece that you can only see\nfrom one vantage point."},{"time":116840,"text":"I wanted to challenge myself artistically\nby painting over several buildings"},{"time":121200,"text":"and having it only fully visible\nfrom one point on the Muqattam Mountain."},{"time":126360,"text":"The Muqattam Mountain\nis the pride of the community."},{"time":128960,"text":"This is where they built\nthe St. Simon Monastery,"},{"time":131440,"text":"a 10,000-seat cave church\nthat they carved into the mountain itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137200,"text":"So, the first time\nI stood on top of the mountain"},{"time":141280,"text":"and I looked at the neighborhood,"},{"time":142920,"text":"I asked myself, how on earth\nwill I convince all those owners"},{"time":145840,"text":"to let me paint on their buildings?"},{"time":148040,"text":"And then Magd came."},{"time":149440,"text":"Magd is a guide from the Church."},{"time":151840,"text":"He told me the only person I needed\nto convince was Father Samaan,"},{"time":155960,"text":"who is the leader of the community."},{"time":158440,"text":"But to convince Father Samaan,\nI needed to convince Mario,"},{"time":161680,"text":"who is a Polish artist\nwho moved to Cairo 20 years ago"},{"time":164760,"text":"and who created all the artwork\nof the Cave Church."},{"time":168600,"text":"I am really grateful to Mario.\nHe was the key of the project."},{"time":172280,"text":"He managed to get me\na meeting with Father Samaan,"},{"time":174680,"text":"and surprisingly, he loved the idea."},{"time":176440,"text":"He asked me about where I painted before"},{"time":178720,"text":"and how I will make it happen."},{"time":180200,"text":"And he was mainly concerned\nby what I was going to write."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184760,"text":"In every work that I create,\nI write messages"},{"time":186920,"text":"with my style of Arabic calligraphy."},{"time":188720,"text":"I make sure those messages are relevant\nto the place where I am painting"},{"time":192480,"text":"but have this universal dimension,"},{"time":194124,"text":"so anybody around the world\ncan relate to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197560,"text":"So for Manshiyat Naser,"},{"time":198840,"text":"I decided to write in Arabic\nthe words of St. Athanasius of Alexandria,"},{"time":203640,"text":"a Coptic bishop from the third century,"},{"time":205600,"text":"who said: (Arabic),"},{"time":210200,"text":"which means in English,"},{"time":211480,"text":"\"Anyone who wants\nto see the sunlight clearly"},{"time":213640,"text":"needs to wipe his eyes first.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":215800,"text":"It was really important for me"},{"time":217600,"text":"that the community\nfelt connected to the words."},{"time":220520,"text":"And for me this quote was perfectly\nreflecting the spirit of the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224480,"text":"So Father Samaan blessed the project,"},{"time":226920,"text":"and his approval brought\nall the residents on board."},{"time":230640,"text":"Hundreds of liters of paint,\na dozen blue manual lifts,"},{"time":234960,"text":"several trips back and forth to Cairo,"},{"time":237120,"text":"a strong and solid team from France,\nNorth Africa, Middle East and the US,"},{"time":241280,"text":"and after a year of planning\nand logistics, there we are,"},{"time":244760,"text":"my team and some members\nfrom the local community"},{"time":247400,"text":"creating a piece that will\nspread over 50 buildings,"},{"time":250920,"text":"some filling up the space\nof the calligraphy"},{"time":253840,"text":"that I trace with colors."},{"time":255280,"text":"Here some blue, there some yellow,\nthere some orange."},{"time":258360,"text":"Some others carrying some sand bags"},{"time":260519,"text":"and putting them\non the top of the buildings"},{"time":262640,"text":"to hold those manual lifts,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and some others assembling\nand disassembling those same lifts"},{"time":266920,"text":"and moving them around\nthe different buildings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270200,"text":"At the beginning of the project,"},{"time":271920,"text":"I numbered all those\nbuildings on my sketch,"},{"time":275600,"text":"and there was no real interaction\nwith the community."},{"time":278120,"text":"People didn’t get the point of all this."},{"time":280280,"text":"But fast enough, those building numbers\nbecame family names."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284800,"text":"The first building\nwas the house of Uncle Ibrahim."},{"time":288040,"text":"Uncle Ibrahim is such\nan enthusiastic person."},{"time":290200,"text":"He was always singing and making jokes,"},{"time":292280,"text":"and his daughters and sons\nsaved me from his bull"},{"time":296640,"text":"who wanted to attack me\non the fourth floor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":300440,"text":"Actually, the bull saw me from the window\nand came out on the balcony."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305120,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309680,"text":"Uncle Ibrahim was always\nhanging out on the balcony"},{"time":312360,"text":"and talking to me while I was painting."},{"time":314360,"text":"I remember him saying that he didn’t\ngo to the mountain for 10 years,"},{"time":318360,"text":"and that he never takes a day off."},{"time":320200,"text":"He said that if he stopped working,\nwho will stop the garbage?"},{"time":324000,"text":"But surprisingly,\nat the end of the project,"},{"time":327440,"text":"he came all the way to the mountain\nto look at the piece."},{"time":330280,"text":"He was really proud\nto see his house painted,"},{"time":333080,"text":"and he said that this project\nwas a project of peace and --"},{"time":338400,"text":"sorry --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354400,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356320,"text":"He said that it was a project\nof peace and unity"},{"time":361320,"text":"and that it brought people together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363680,"text":"So his perception\ntowards the project changed,"},{"time":366920,"text":"and my perception towards\nthe community changed also,"},{"time":370840,"text":"and towards what they do."},{"time":372800,"text":"All the garbage that everybody\nis disgusted by is not theirs."},{"time":377440,"text":"They just work out of it."},{"time":378960,"text":"Actually, they don’t live in the garbage.\nThey live from the garbage."},{"time":382240,"text":"So I started doubting myself and wondering"},{"time":384480,"text":"what was the real purpose\nof this whole project?"},{"time":388280,"text":"It was not about beautifying\na place by bringing art to it."},{"time":392400,"text":"It was about switching perception\nand opening a dialogue"},{"time":395480,"text":"on the connection that we have\nwith communities that we don’t know."},{"time":399520,"text":"So day after day,"},{"time":400800,"text":"the calligraphy circle was taking shape,"},{"time":403200,"text":"and we were always excited to go back\non the mountain to look at the piece."},{"time":407280,"text":"And standing exactly at this point\nevery day made my realize"},{"time":410440,"text":"the symbolism behind\nthis anamorphic piece."},{"time":413280,"text":"If you want to see\nthe real image of somebody,"},{"time":415480,"text":"maybe you should change your angle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418440,"text":"There was doubts and difficulties,"},{"time":420280,"text":"like fears and stress."},{"time":421560,"text":"It wasn't simple\nto work in such environments,"},{"time":423760,"text":"sometimes having pigs under you\nwhile you paint"},{"time":426000,"text":"or climbing a stack of garbage\nto reach a lift."},{"time":428840,"text":"But we all got over the fear\nof the heights, the swinging lifts,"},{"time":432200,"text":"the strength of the smell"},{"time":433480,"text":"and also the stress\nof not finishing on time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435640,"text":"But the kindness of all those people\nmade us forget everything."},{"time":439600,"text":"The building number 3 was the house\nof Uncle Bakheet and Aunty Fareeda."},{"time":443800,"text":"In Egyptian, they have\nthis expression that says, \"Ahsen Nas,\""},{"time":447080,"text":"which means \"the best people.\""},{"time":448640,"text":"They were the best people."},{"time":449920,"text":"We used to take our break\nin front of their houses,"},{"time":453080,"text":"and all the kids of the neighborhood"},{"time":455480,"text":"used to join us."},{"time":456840,"text":"I was impressed and amazed\nby the kids of Manshiyat Naser."},{"time":461200,"text":"For the first few days, they were always\nrefusing anything we were offering them,"},{"time":465360,"text":"even a snack or a drink."},{"time":467440,"text":"So I asked Aunty Fareeda, \"Why is that?\""},{"time":469400,"text":"And she told me they teach\ntheir kids to refuse anything"},{"time":473280,"text":"from somebody that they don't know"},{"time":474960,"text":"because maybe this person\nneeds it more than they do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478880,"text":"So at this exact point I realized actually"},{"time":482920,"text":"the Zaraeeb community\nwas the ideal context"},{"time":485080,"text":"to raise the topic of perception."},{"time":487240,"text":"We need to question\nour level of misconception"},{"time":490560,"text":"and judgment we can have as a society"},{"time":493240,"text":"upon communities\nbased on their differences."},{"time":496960,"text":"I remember how we got delayed\non Uncle Ibrahim's house"},{"time":500440,"text":"when his pigs that are bred on the rooftop"},{"time":502600,"text":"were eating the sand bags\nthat hold the lifts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":507640,"text":"The house of Uncle Bakheet\nand Aunty Fareeda"},{"time":510600,"text":"was this kind of meeting point."},{"time":512280,"text":"Everybody used to gather there."},{"time":514159,"text":"I think this is what Uncle Ibrahim meant"},{"time":516120,"text":"when he said that was\na project of peace and unity,"},{"time":518760,"text":"because I really felt\nthat people were coming together."},{"time":522320,"text":"Everyone was greeting us\nwith a smile, offering us a drink"},{"time":525520,"text":"or inviting us into their\nown house for lunch."},{"time":529560,"text":"Sometime, you are\nat the first level of a building,"},{"time":532600,"text":"and somebody opens his window\nand offers you some tea."},{"time":535160,"text":"And then the same thing happens\non the second floor."},{"time":537640,"text":"And you keep going all the way to the top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540920,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":542400,"text":"I think I never drink as much tea\nas I did in Egypt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544880,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":546720,"text":"And to be honest with you,\nwe could have finished earlier,"},{"time":549480,"text":"but I think it took us three weeks\nbecause of all those tea breaks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":556520,"text":"In Egypt, they have another expression,\nwhich is \"Nawartouna,\""},{"time":560080,"text":"which means, \"You brought light to us.\""},{"time":563200,"text":"In Manshiyat Naser\nthey were always telling us this."},{"time":566120,"text":"The calligraphy, actually --"},{"time":568280,"text":"I used a white glow-in-the-dark paint\nfor the calligraphy"},{"time":572360,"text":"so at the end of the project,\nwe rented some black light projectors"},{"time":576560,"text":"and lit up the whole neighborhood,"},{"time":578960,"text":"surprising everybody around."},{"time":580360,"text":"We wanted to tell them"},{"time":581640,"text":"that they are the ones\nwho brought light to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"The Zaraeeb community\nare strong, honest, hard workers,"},{"time":601080,"text":"and they know their value."},{"time":602840,"text":"The people of Cairo\ncall them \"the Zabaleen,\""},{"time":605000,"text":"which means \"the people of the garbage,\""},{"time":607000,"text":"but ironically,\nthe people of Manshiyat Naser"},{"time":609760,"text":"call the people of Cairo the Zabaleen."},{"time":611640,"text":"They say, they are the ones\nwho produce the garbage, not them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":615840,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617240,"text":"The goal was to leave something\nto this community,"},{"time":619640,"text":"but I feel that they are the ones\nwho left something in our lives."},{"time":622800,"text":"You know, the art project\nwas just a pretext"},{"time":624920,"text":"for this amazing human experience."},{"time":626600,"text":"The art piece at some point\nwill disappear, vanish,"},{"time":629040,"text":"and actually there is somebody\nwho is building a second floor"},{"time":631960,"text":"in front of Uncle Ibrahim's house,"},{"time":633640,"text":"so it's covering part of the painting,"},{"time":635520,"text":"so I might need to go back\nand paint over it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":639320,"text":"It was about the experience,"},{"time":640720,"text":"about the story,"},{"time":642160,"text":"about the moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644560,"text":"From the streets of the neighborhood,"},{"time":646480,"text":"the painting appears in fragments,"},{"time":648124,"text":"isolated from one another,"},{"time":650040,"text":"standing alone."},{"time":651320,"text":"But connected with the sign of calligraphy"},{"time":653520,"text":"that today reveals the powerful message\nthat we should all think about"},{"time":657400,"text":"before we want to judge somebody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659640,"text":"Anyone who wants to see\nthe sunlight clearly"},{"time":661800,"text":"needs to wipe his eyes first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663760,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}